# CoinGecko Demo API key. Set this locally (.env) and in your host
# (e.g. Vercel -> Project -> Settings -> Environment Variables) so the
# site ships with a pre-configured key and users don't need to paste
# one into the Settings drawer.
#
# Get a free Demo key at https://www.coingecko.com/en/developers/dashboard
#
# Note: Vite inlines VITE_* variables into the client bundle at build time,
# so whatever you put here is visible to anyone viewing the deployed page's
# source. That's fine for a Demo-tier key on an internal tool; for a public
# production deploy, proxy CoinGecko through a small backend instead.
VITE_COINGECKO_API_KEY=CG-your-demo-key-here
